  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2010-09-28",
    "date": "2010-12-06T22:35:23Z",
    "text": "Inform All Veterans Act - Directs the Secretary of Veterans Affairs (VA), as part of outreach services provided to veterans, to make available at readily accessible locations in VA health care facilities, and to ask each visiting veteran if that veteran wishes to receive, written information concerning: (1) submitting a claim for compensation; (2) establishing a service connection for a disability; and (3) contact information about VA offices that may offer assistance with respect to service-connected disabilities."
  },
